message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
🎮🐉🎲𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘥𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘳𝘰𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘪𝘤𝘦 𝘰𝘯 𝘢 𝘣𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘥-𝘯𝘦𝘸 𝘺𝘦𝘢𝘳?⭐

During the 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐲, FEU Tech SAGE unveiled our 𝐀𝐕𝐏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒.𝐘. 𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟓–𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟔!✨

Whether it’s game development, tabletop quests, casual matches, or epic campaigns, you’ll find a home right here in 𝐒𝐀𝐆𝐄. ⚔️👾

Here’s to a year filled with games, stories, and camaraderie. 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐲! 🕹️🦦💙

#FITSAGE2526
#SAGE2526
#PassionIntoProgress
#JoinSAGE

🎬 Director: Allen Alwin David
🎨 Co-director, VA, Assets: Arianna Salumbides
🎞️ Editor: John Leland Miñon
📝 Caption: Ina Bautista

🎵 Music: It’s Going Down Now — Lotus Juice & Azumi Takahashi, composed by Atsushi Kitajoh

message.text:
🎮🐉🎲𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘥𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘳𝘰𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘪𝘤𝘦 𝘰𝘯 𝘢 𝘣𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘥-𝘯𝘦𝘸 𝘺𝘦𝘢𝘳?⭐

During the 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐲, FEU Tech SAGE unveiled our 𝐀𝐕𝐏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒.𝐘. 𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟓–𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟔!✨

Whether it’s game development, tabletop quests, casual matches, or epic campaigns, you’ll find a home right here in 𝐒𝐀𝐆𝐄. ⚔️👾

Here’s to a year filled with games, stories, and camaraderie. 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐲! 🕹️🦦💙

#FITSAGE2526
#SAGE2526
#PassionIntoProgress
#JoinSAGE

🎬 Director: Allen Alwin David
🎨 Co-director, VA, Assets: Arianna Salumbides
🎞️ Editor: John Leland Miñon
📝 Caption: Ina Bautista

🎵 Music: It’s Going Down Now — Lotus Juice & Azumi Takahashi, composed by Atsushi Kitajoh

message.text:
🎮🐉🎲𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘥𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘳𝘰𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘪𝘤𝘦 𝘰𝘯 𝘢 𝘣𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘥-𝘯𝘦𝘸 𝘺𝘦𝘢𝘳?⭐

During the 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐲, FEU Tech SAGE unveiled our 𝐀𝐕𝐏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒.𝐘. 𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟓–𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟔!✨

Whether it’s game development, tabletop quests, casual matches, or epic campaigns, you’ll find a home right here in 𝐒𝐀𝐆𝐄. ⚔️👾

Here’s to a year filled with games, stories, and camaraderie. 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐲! 🕹️🦦💙

#FITSAGE2526
#SAGE2526
#PassionIntoProgress
#JoinSAGE

🎬 Director: Allen Alwin David
🎨 Co-director, VA, Assets: Arianna Salumbides
🎞️ Editor: John Leland Miñon
📝 Caption: Ina Bautista

🎵 Music: It’s Going Down Now — Lotus Juice & Azumi Takahashi, composed by Atsushi Kitajoh

message.text:
🎮🐉🎲𝘙𝘦𝘢𝘥𝘺 𝘵𝘰 𝘳𝘰𝘭𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘪𝘤𝘦 𝘰𝘯 𝘢 𝘣𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘥-𝘯𝘦𝘸 𝘺𝘦𝘢𝘳?⭐

During the 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐲, FEU Tech SAGE unveiled our 𝐀𝐕𝐏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐒.𝐘. 𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟓–𝟐𝟓𝟐𝟔!✨

Whether it’s game development, tabletop quests, casual matches, or epic campaigns, you’ll find a home right here in 𝐒𝐀𝐆𝐄. ⚔️👾

Here’s to a year filled with games, stories, and camaraderie. 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐲! 🕹️🦦💙

#FITSAGE2526
#SAGE2526
#PassionIntoProgress
#JoinSAGE

🎬 Director: Allen Alwin David
🎨 Co-director, VA, Assets: Arianna Salumbides
🎞️ Editor: John Leland Miñon
📝 Caption: Ina Bautista

🎵 Music: It’s Going Down Now — Lotus Juice & Azumi Takahashi, composed by Atsushi Kitajoh
